.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-6::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, disco, rock, gospel
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rugby, badminton, baseball, tennis
1. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
2. the fan of gospel is the person who's sport is baseball##1
3. the fan of gospel is on the far right##1
4. the fan of disco is the person who's sport is rugby##1
5. the fan of rock is between the fan of electronic and the fan of disco##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | disco     | rock           | electronic | gospel  |
| Sport         | rugby | tennis | badminton   | baseball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, blues, dubstep, r&b
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, quad-bike, boat, scooter
1. the fan of blues is the person driving the ship##1
2. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
3. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the fan of ambient##1
4. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
5. the fan of ambient is between the person driving the ship and the fan of dubstep##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | r&b   | blues | ambient | dubstep      |
| Transport     | boat | ship    | quad-bike  | scooter |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-8::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, basketball, rowing, handball
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, quad-bike, subway, boat
1. the person driving the taxi is the person who's sport is basketball##1
2. the person driving the quad-bike is between the person who's sport is rowing and the person driving the subway##2
3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the taxi is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |       2       |     3      |     4      |
| Sport       | sailing | handball | rowing     | basketball   |
| Transport   | subway   | quad-bike     | boat | taxi |

