.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  software-developer, analyst, musician, nurse
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, car, taxi, motorbike
1. the musician is between the person driving the jet-ski and the software-developer##2
2. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the software-developer##1
3. the nurse is on the right of the software-developer##1
4. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
5. the software-developer is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |      4       |
| Job         | analyst | musician | software-developer | nurse |
| Transport   | jet-ski         | motorbike       | car    | taxi         |

