.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-10::.
There 4 different types of food: strawberry, kale, pomegranate, grapefruit
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, badminton, rowing, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person eating grapefruit##1
2. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1
3. the person eating strawberry is on the right of the person eating kale##1
4. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
5. the person who's sport is badminton is between the person eating kale and the person who's sport is volleyball##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Food    | grapefruit   | pomegranate      | kale   | strawberry  |
| Sport   | volleyball | badminton | rowing | biathlon |

