.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-11::.
There 4 different types of food: pumpkin, pineapple, carrot, cranberry
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, satire, horror, disaster
1. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
2. the person eating pineapple is between the person eating cranberry and the person eating pumpkin##2
3. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
4. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |      4      |
| Food          | pumpkin     | pineapple | cranberry   | carrot        |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | horror   | satire | disaster |

