.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-12::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, baking, sudoku, fishing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, reggae, classical, folk
1. the fan of classical is the person who's hobby is baking##1
2. the fan of reggae is on the left of the fan of folk##1
3. the fan of country is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the fan of reggae##1
5. the fan of country is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
6. the fan of reggae is between the person who's hobby is baking and the person who's hobby is fishing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | baking | sudoku | fishing | woodworking |
| Music-Genre   | classical          | reggae     | folk  | country     |

