.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-17::.
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, turkish, russian, japanese
4 different pets are kept: rat, snake, hamster, horse
1. the canadian is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
2. the japanese is the owner of the hamster##1
3. the owner of the snake is between the owner of the rat and the turkish##2
4. the owner of the horse is the owner of the horse##1
5. the owner of the horse is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Nationality   | japanese | turkish | canadian | russian |
| Pet           | hamster  | horse  | snake | rat      |

