The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, surfing, rugby, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
3. the thai is the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
4. the person who's sport is volleyball is between the spanish and the turkish##2
5. the turkish is the person who's sport is rugby##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | thai   | spanish   | indian | turkish |
| Sport         | skateboarding | surfing | volleyball     | rugby    |

