.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, photography, board-games, traveling
4 different pets are kept: rat, hedgehog, bird, dog
1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is baking is between the owner of the rat and the person who's hobby is traveling##2
3. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
4. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | board-games    | traveling     | baking | photography |
| Pet     | hedgehog | dog | bird       | rat     |

 